                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <span class="ml-auto text-xs text-slate-400">Hace 2 sem</span>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">"Increíble experiencia. Los guías fueron super atentos y el paisaje es de otro planeta. Vale cada centavo."</p>
                        </div>
                        <!-- Review Card 2 -->
                        <div class="p-5 rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700 shadow-sm">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                                <div class="size-10 rounded-full bg-slate-200 overflow-hidden">
                                    <img alt="User avatar" class="w-full h-full object-cover" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAhns1xrllTdCMAR6-IDTrx9AyFmseIL-RdnWMdCGaxx03QmUQz4QkKbkzZCKNLY1QgnyJ5bR4kqt7zsTO8Ik8C2bJI9Vj-KfkPHIkBW45_SsaPKTpYJzrxRqSW-NcWjOUQ4qJSa93VSzeVGTDXel4qzXTp4IpBtzddpjQDF7-K_aOIPbbqRC-c0GkdnMHPEh4G46Ownf8MdouHpgiDE_5j7R7L3YZjY59QgeN9ks9JrnslmdiVQfE4ldQFOerhlh9XCxfIr5cXpl4" />
